title: Redfish Power Consumption
agents: agent_redfish
catalog: hw/server/redfish
license: GPLv2
distribution: check_mk
description:
 This check monitors power consumption metrics from Redfish compatible devices.
 It tracks average, minimum, and maximum consumed watts per system.
 Graphs are available for up to 4 systems (member IDs 0 through 3).
 Systems beyond this limit are still monitored but without graph definitions.

discovery:
 One service is created for each power control entry with power consumption data.

item:
 The member ID of the power control entry.
